Articles.Content:
As you may guess from the post title, i have a problem with timewarp causing me to los performance. 

Whenever i engage timewarp, FPS drops down to 1ps, in the highest gear. I have about 5FPS on 1k timewarp. 
This coincidentally met with deepfreeze telling me i dont have enough electricity on my craft ot keep one kerbal frozen, despite having 20k EC and a reactor from USI. 
Does anyone have any idea, if that is the issue? Before i do anything drastic and purge my KSP directory.
